    <item>
      <title>Clever Kubernetes Operator v0.7.0 with wider products support</title>
      <link>//localhost:1313/changelog/2025/03-31-kunernetes-operator-0.7.0/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>//localhost:1313/changelog/2025/03-31-kunernetes-operator-0.7.0/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/CleverCloud/clever-kubernetes-operator/releases/tag/v0.6.0&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Clever Kubernetes Operator v0.7.0&lt;/a&gt; is available. It now uses &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/CleverCloud/clevercloud-sdk-rust/releases/tag/v0.15.0&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;clevercloud-sdk-rust v0.15.0&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/CleverCloud/oauth10a-rust/releases/tag/v2.1.1&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;oauth10a v2.1.1&lt;/a&gt;. It fixes some bugs, comes with updated documentation and PostgreSQL versions. If you&amp;rsquo;re connected to &lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:1313/developers/doc/cli&#34; &gt;Clever Tools&lt;/a&gt;, credentials are automatically detected and used with this release. &lt;a href=&#34;https://azimutt.app/docs&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Azimutt&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:1313/developers/doc/addons/cellar&#34; &gt;Cellar&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:1313/developers/doc/addons/keycloak&#34; &gt;Keycloak&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:1313/developers/doc/addons/matomo&#34; &gt;Matomo&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:1313/developers/doc/addons/otoroshi&#34; &gt;Otoroshi&lt;/a&gt; can now be deployed as custom resources.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:1313/developers/guides/kubernetes-operator&#34; &gt;Learn more about Clever Kubernetes Operator&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

      </description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
