      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/CleverCloud/clever-kubernetes-operator/releases/tag/v0.6.0&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Clever Kubernetes Operator v0.6.0&lt;/a&gt; is available. It now uses &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/CleverCloud/clevercloud-sdk-rust/releases/tag/v0.12.0&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;clevercloud-sdk-rust v0.12.0&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/CleverCloud/oauth10a-rust/releases/tag/v2.0.0&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;oauth10a v2.0.0&lt;/a&gt; to simplify authentication through API Tokens or Basic Auth. This release also adds Materia KV add-ons support as custom resource.&lt;/p&gt;
